item.description: NH's Constitutional Scholar Dianne Gilbert will be presenting information on your rights under the NH Constitution as well as our Federal Constitution. She will also discuss the limits of Federal Government as well as State Government. Dianne is brilliant and we will have a Q&A as usual.  I am going to be handing out the "Are You Ready" handouts that are quite detailed and with some added recommendations on what you may need in case of any type of emergency.
item.name: Dianne Gilbert on NH State & Federal Constitutions also Preparedness Manual
